               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; incipit of the sections of the text (a homily, absolution prayer, miracle and ʿarke); selected words and lines in Texts I-II; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
